OL,5, Pope Francis has held a private meeting
OL,6, with victims of clerical sexual abuse  
OL,7, during a five-day visit to Portugal.   
OL,9,FIn a statement, the Vatican said the   
OL,10,Fgathering had been held on Wednesday in
OL,11,Fan "atmosphere of intense listening".  
OL,13,FA report this year concluded that at   
OL,14,Fleast 4,815 children had been abused in
OL,15,FPortugal and that the Church had sought
OL,16,F"systematically" to conceal the issue. 
OL,18,FAt an evening service in Lisbon, the   
OL,19,FPope said the Church must listen to    
OL,20,F"the anguished cry of the victims".    
